2.4.3
  - fixed typo https://github.com/igorkasyanchuk/rails_db/pull/136/files
  - fix for Rails 7.1 https://github.com/igorkasyanchuk/rails_db/pull/139/files
  - added dependency of sprockets-rails to fix issue with Rails 7.1 (assets.precompile files)
