2.4.2
  - ransack fix https://github.com/igorkasyanchuk/rails_db/pull/132

2.4.1
  - Fix zeitwerk deprecation warning https://github.com/igorkasyanchuk/rails_db/pull/123/files
  - Fix for country field (show as string instead of using simple_form:country_select)

2.4.0
  - added sandbox option https://github.com/igorkasyanchuk/rails_db/pull/122 (virtual360-io)
  - fixing tests and moving to new travis domain
  - dummy app run with rails 6

2.3.0, 2.3.1
  - drop support Rails 5.2, 5.1, 5.0 (for older user version 2.2.1 of this gem)
  - required versions of gems (will_paginate >= 3.1, ransack >= 2.3.2)
  - fixed issue with ransack for Rails 6 and new ransack
  - migration to caxlsx / caxlsx-rails

2.2.0 + 2.2.1
  - use more secure version of Simple Form (>= 5.0.1)
  - use smaller amount of JS from codemirror
  - upgraded codemirror to 5.49.2
  - fixed SQL hit for SQL (now shows columns)
  - other minor gems upgrades

2.1.0
  - now using newer version of CodeMirror (bundled inside Rails DB)
  - support Rails 6
  - simplified matrix of tests on Travis CI (removed Rails 5.0, 5.1 from tests, but they are still supported)

2.0.6
  - require activerecord (to support non-RoR apps)

2.0.5
  - allow newer version of simple_form

2.0.4
  - support for simple_form 4.0+ only
  - added support for "tsvector" field type

2.0.3
  - fix for namespaces (e.g. /admin/tools/rails_db)

2.0
  - drop Rails 4.x support
  - verified support for Ruby 2.3+
  - removed not needed code

1.6
  - Bugfixes

1.4.0 - January 24, 2017
  - works with Rails 6
  - upgraded ransack
  - fixed STI

1.1 - December 31, 2015
  - code cleanup
  - bug fixes and optimizations (thanks @bbenezech)

1.0 - December 2, 2015
  - add CREATE functionality support
  - show query SQL in popup
  - code cleanup

0.9.9 - November 29, 2015
  - add search using http://railscasts.com/episodes/370-ransack?autoplay=true
  - add sorting/filters to data-tables (filters in header, multiple, <,=,>,LIKE,NOT LIKE, etc)
  - changing link in browser (on ajax calls, so F5 refresh will work)
  - bix fixes

0.9 - November 24, 2015
  - edit content in table
  - bug fixes
  - added method 'as_model' to return ActiveRecord model to simplify future development

0.8 - November 18, 2015
  - added show/hide for table columns
  - added export to XLS
  - bug fixes

0.7 - November 1, 2015
  - added standalone app 'railsdb'
  - added util app 'runsql'
  - scroll page to Table Data if we have many tables and user click in sidebar on it
  - disable logs for standalone apps

0.6 - October 28, 2015
  - better results if no results
  - add truncate table
  - add information about indexes
  - fixed issue with helpers (thanks @losadaem)
  - added delete for records (by PK)
  - added information about primary key

0.5.1 - October 27, 2015
  - removed log files and other garbage to reduce size of gem

0.5 - October 26, 2015
  - added config.verify_access_proc to make possible enable access for users (for example current_user.admin?)
  - small tweaks to rails_db_data_table and rails_db_data_sql
  - other minor fixes
  - working on documentation

